title: Camp WeWow - Scat Week Day 5: Party Poopers!

It's Day 5 of Scat Week, and we're hearing from campers who called in! To print your Scatvenger badge, head to tinkercast.com/camp. Want to catch up from episodes of Camp WeWow? Head to our new "WeWow" feed to listen now! Then, come back next Monday for brand new episodes of Camp WeWow!
